description: Tattooed, muscular Vadim Black and beefy, dark-haired Damien Stone are getting ready for a double date that Damien set up. Little did they know, Damien’s date didn’t have someone for Vadim, but instead wanted to be able to choose between both men. Unimpressed by her tactics, the good-looking, hung and horny men dismiss her, and decide to fuck each other instead!
title: Who's The Real Catch
